    "question_id" : 79572434,
    "body" : "<p>You don't have to specify anything in the config file, by default MCP logs are saved in the following directories</p>\n<p><strong>Windows</strong></p>\n<p><code>%appdata%/Claude/logs</code></p>\n<p><strong>Mac</strong></p>\n<p><code>~/Library/Logs/Claude/mcp*.log</code></p>\n<p>For more, read their official documentation here <a href=\"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/docs/tools/debugging\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">MCP debugging</a></p>\n",
